quran[18{c,v,t}:
98,8,"unn ki jaza unn ke Rab ke haan daimi qiyam ki jannaten hain jin ke neechay nhrin bah rahi hon gi, woh un mein hamesha hamesha rahen ge Allah un se raazi howa aur woh Allah se raazi hue yeh kuch hai uss shakhs ke liye jis ne apne Rab ka khauf kya ho"
99,1,jab zameen apni poori shiddat ke sath hila daali jaye gi
99,2,aur zameen apne andar ke saaray boojh nikaal kar bahar daal day gi
99,3,aur ensaan kahe ga ke yeh iss ko kya ho raha hai
99,4,uss roz woh apne ( oopar guzray hue ) halaat bayan kere gi
99,5,kyunkay tairay Rab ne ussay ( aysakrne ka ) hukum diya hoga
99,6,uss roz log mutafarraq haalat mein pultain ge taakay unn ke aamaal unn ko dukhaay jayen
99,7,phir jis ne zarra baRabar neki ki hogi woh is ko dekh le ga
99,8,aur jis ne zarra baRabar badi ki hogi woh is ko dekh le ga
100,1,qasam hai unn ( ghoron ) ki jo phunkaray maartay hue dorrtay hain
100,2,phir ( apni taapon se ) chingariya chotayhain
100,3,phir subah saweray chhapa maartay hain
100,4,phir is mauqa par gird o gubhar uratay hain
100,5,phir aِsi haalat mein kisi majmaa ke andar ja gustay hain
100,6,haqeeqat yeh hai ke ensaan apne Rab ka bara nashukara hai
100,7,aur woh khud iss par gawah hai
100,8,aur woh maal o doulat ki mohabbat mein buri terhan mubtala hai
100,9,to kya woh uss haqeeqat ko nahi jaanta jab qabron mein jo kuch ( madfoon ) hai ussay nikaal liya jaye ga
